data.description:
Welcome to your new home at Colonnade Lofts in the heart of Denver's historic Cheesman Park subdivision! This stunning 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo offers a perfect blend of historic charm and modern convenience.

As you step into this timeless condo, you'll be greeted by charming exposed brick walls, decorative fireplace, and beautiful original wood trim, creating an ambiance of elegance and warmth. The updated kitchen boasts granite countertops, mid-mod cabinets, and opens to the dining/living space. Hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the space, complementing the historic character while providing easy maintenance.

Relax and unwind on the balcony, overlooking the gated courtyard with a fire pit, community garden, and convenient bike storage. The location is prime for convenience and very walkable with everything Denver has to offer is just steps away. Explore Cheesman Park, City Park, or the vibrant 17th Avenue bars and restaurants. Downtown Denver, shops, cafes, boutique gyms, live music venues, and cultural attractions are all within walking distance from the lofts, offering unparalleled convenience and entertainment options.

This condo also offers modern amenities for your comfort, including a NEW water heater (2021), NEW AC (2022), and Washer /Dryer in the Primary Bedroom. With it's hot location and exceptional features, this condo is the epitome of Denver living at its finest. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming retreat your new home! Schedule a showing today and experience the allure of Colonnade Lofts living for yourself.
